<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        background: #0f0f0f;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0033 0%, #2a003f 100%);
        padding: 40px 50px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        max-width: 600px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(92, 26, 155, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #e9d5ff;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      p {
        color: #d8b4fe;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .logo svg {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
      }
      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          transparent 0%,
          #7e22ce 50%,
          transparent 100%
        );
        margin: 25px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #a78bfa;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path
            d="M12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5228 6.47715 22 12 22Z"
            stroke="#C084FC"
            stroke-width="2"
          />
          <path
            d="M12 16V16.01M12 8V12"
            stroke="#E9D5FF"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
          />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>Welcome, <%= firstName %> <span style="color: #c084fc">ðŸŽ‰</span></h1>
      <p>
        Thanks for joining Tevah! We're excited to have you on board and can't
        wait to see what we'll accomplish together.
      </p>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #8b5cf6">
          Bashorn Okunsnya | Lekki Aso | All Shades of Purple
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
